$NetBSD: patch-configure,v 1.5 2024/10/14 13:04:00 adam Exp $

Skip compiler detection magic.

Avoid choosing aligned_alloc() when it's not present, such as CentOS 6
with lang/gcc7 and older Solaris releases.

